HEADWORD: Punctator
<hw>Punc*ta"tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who marks with
points. specifically, one who writes Hebrew with points; -- applied to a
Masorite.</def> <rj><au>E. Robinson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

